WEBVTT

00:07:29.260 --> 00:07:32.640
(Applause)

00:07:32.640 --> 00:07:38.519
Indian festivals, culture, our identity,
our prayers, our language, our clothes,

00:07:38.520 --> 00:07:43.569
our celebrations, our wealth,
our poverty is all in the book.

00:07:43.569 --> 00:07:48.319
For the first time in history at Cannes
Film Festival, a book was launched in 2015.

00:07:48.320 --> 00:07:55.320
It was presented to President Barack Obama
Prime Minister Modi, H. H. Dalai Lama,

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:59.919
President Clinton, Mark Zuckerberg, 
Pope Francis, and recently I was invited

00:07:59.919 --> 00:08:03.120
to the Buckingham Palace 
to present the book to the Queen.